                            [Sam Longley]                             
                                                                        
                                                                      
                                                                        
   Actor/comedian (and brother of Anna's hubby Luc) Sam Longley drops    
    by the kitchen for a chat and quickie cook-off. Aptly named, the     
    6'10 Sam towers over his sister-in-law. The banter is cheeky and     
   relaxed as Sam shares memories and career anecdotes, including his    
   2006 experience donning a 50 kilogram monster suit to play Ira in     
   the Spike Jonze film Where the Wild Things Are. After making Anna     
    a warm-up margarita, Sam whips up one of his favourites: tequila     
   tortillas with prawns and paprika. Anna cooks an oriental quickie     
    of Balinese chicken with snake beans, followed by a kid-friendly     
      quickie of spaghetti and meatballs and finishes off with an        
              adults-only quickie of walnut and rum torte.
